import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Link,NavLink, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; const MainNavbar = () => { const [isProfileMenuOpen, setIsProfileMenuOpen] = useState(false); const [logoutSuccess, setLogoutSuccess] = useState(false); // State to track logout success const navigate = useNavigate(); const toggleProfileMenu = () => { setIsProfileMenuOpen(!isProfileMenuOpen); }; const handleLogout = () => { localStorage.removeItem('userEmail'); // Example, if you store a token in localStorage localStorage.removeItem('userToken'); // Set logout success state setLogoutSuccess(true); // Redirect to login screen after 2 seconds setTimeout(() => { setLogoutSuccess(false); // Hide the message after redirecting navigate('/admin-head-login'); // Redirect to admin login }, 2000); }; useEffect(() => { // Simulate user data fetch and storage in localStorage const userName = localStorage.getItem('userName'); if (!userName) { localStorage.setItem('userName', 'OVI'); localStorage.setItem('userEmail', 'oviashriv@gmail.com'); localStorage.setItem('userRole', 'Admin'); } }, []); return (
